        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">You still have a chance to max those skills and you are at just the right lvl. I recently maxed out my defense, offense and piercing by fighting SF's alongside my trusty pet. For defence I just waded in from the start. As long as you keep BOD up all the time and maybe even turn Lich off you shouldn't have a problem staying alive. When you back off to refresh BOD they go straight back to the pet. For the offensive skills it was easier to wait until they turn for the death walk, dark them and call pet off. You can get quite a few shots in before they drop.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
